0/extras/21cd9d4b1767531b7531f121e73e5e29.mp4?t=1765821813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/05c2dbcdbf87407e3dd4181746a31d28.apng?t=1765821813\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/05c2dbcdbf87407e3dd4181746a31d28.poster.avif?t=1765821813\" class=\"bb_img\" width=512 height=125 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/8562575aaa8a65c342765b3f4ff2a120.apng?t=1765821813\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/8562575aaa8a65c342765b3f4ff2a120.poster.avif?t=1765821813\" class=\"bb_img\" width=512 height=125 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/d35b24043fe735a458530aa372fc2f2e.apng?t=1765821813\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/d35b24043fe735a458530aa372fc2f2e.poster.avif?t=1765821813\" class=\"bb_img\" width=512 height=125 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/f710f2598b62636ac9e0ac31e0e7291d.apng?t=1765821813\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/f710f2598b62636ac9e0ac31e0e7291d.poster.avif?t=1765821813\" class=\"bb_img\" width=512 height=125 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Features</u></i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore dingy surrealist environments... </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fixed camera horror with light survival elements, use the fixed camera to defeat enemies and solve puzzles... </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Form a pact with a God to ensure your safety...  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
